description: Dante, a supernatural mercenary, must protect an orphaned heiress from demons unleashed by those who desire her estate for themselves.
name: Devil May Cry

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: Dante accepts a mission from Lady to stop a demonically possessed motorcycle named Red Eye that haunts the motorway.
name: Highway Star

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: The mayor’s daughter is secretly dating a man who may be a disguised demon. Dante investigates and becomes entangled in something bigger than just a love affair.
name: Not Love

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: Lady meets up with a strange demon-woman who has a lightning-like technique and a history with Dante.
name: Rolling Thunder

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: A man stalks Dante in hopes of discovering his secrets, and after he spies Dante dispatching demons, the man’s intentions become clear.
name: In Private

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: A group of treasure hunters is being targeted by a female demon that has possessed the body of a former rock star. Only Dante can keep them alive.
name: Rock Queen

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: After a demon grants his tragic wish, a man is locked away for the death of his friend. Dante must take drastic steps to gain the man’s freedom.
name: Wishes Come True

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: Dante is confronted by a man who alleges to have information about the mercenary’s past. Dante must play along with the man’s brutal story while investigating his claim.
name: Once Upon A Time

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: Dante participates in a high stakes game of poker where gamblers are losing a lot more than their money.
name: Death Poker

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: Dante goes head to head with Barusa, a former servant of Sparda. When Barusa’s brother attempts to prevent bloodshed, more violence is the only result.
name: The Last Promise

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: Sid, one of Dante’s most troublesome foes, finally reveals his scheme to unleash chaos and destruction upon humanity.
name: Showtime!

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description: Dante and Sid clash in a final confrontation while the demon invasion threatens to destroy the human world.
name: Stylish!

series.name: Devil May Cry: The Animated Series

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 逆襲！ゼブラ始動!! (Gyakushū! Zebura Shidō!!)

Zebra evens the odds by unleashing the furious power of his voice, Setsuno tangles with an old rival, and Komatsu is shocked to find Toriko on the losing end of a battle!
name: Counterattack! Zebra Starts Up!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: トリコ, 反撃! ｱﾙﾃｨﾒｯﾄﾙｰﾃｨｰﾝ!! (Toriko, Hangeki! Arutimetto Rūtīn!!)

Komatsu’s heartbroken wailing helps revive a battered Toriko, who suddenly unleashes a devastating attack that harnesses the power of a great warrior’s imagination!
name: Toriko Strikes Back! Ultimate Routine!

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic
